io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.entity

Class EntityModificationHelper<T extends org.bukkit.entity.Entity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.entity.EntityModificationHelper<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityAttributeMutator<T>

    public class EntityModificationHelper<T extends org.bukkit.entity.Entity>
extends java.lang.Object
implements EntityAttributeMutator<T>
    Utility class for plugins to be able to modify a specific entity using commands only. For example,

    /mob set [ENTITY_TYPE] - Sets the type of entity. (Create a new EntityModificationHelper)

    /mob modify getName "custom name" - Sets the name of the entity. (call the EntityModification#invokeGetter with the name of the method (getName) and the argument ("custom name"))
